{"tid":199359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"準備好了！衛星圖像顯示北韓即將核試","createTime":"2017-04-13T06:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T07:07:13.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c9a96bc300b19381a8dfaa3a04ce4bba7a6f4b2","tid":199359,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:34:55.000Z","msg":"美國監視北韓武器發展的「北緯38度」(38 North)網站表示，北韓已準備好要在豐溪里(Punggye-ri)核試場進行核子測試。<br />\n<br />\n北緯38度稱，周三的商用衛星影像顯示，豐溪里核試場北邊大門附近持續有活動、主要行政區域有新的活動，且指揮中心附近有一些人在走動。<br />\n<br />\n外界推測，北韓可能正在準備飛彈試射或甚至第6次核子測試，以紀念北韓國父金日成105歲冥壽。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音(Voice of America)引用美國政府與其他消息來源報道，指北韓顯然在隧道中安裝核子裝置，可能會在北韓當地時間15日早上引爆。"},{"pid":"38a03a78629044c7dc3e61261334ff0ed3b45c9a","tid":199359,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0476b24a1ec864a451ecefdd3229fc41fc22f9","tid":199359,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"一般預料，平壤將在北韓「國父」金日成4月15日冥誕，或是4月25日的建軍節當天試射飛彈，甚至進行第6次核試，而這對耐心有限的川普政府來說，無疑將是跨越紅線的行為。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約時報》（The New York Times）報導，專家在檢視衛星圖像後發現，萬塔山（Mount Mantap）有大範圍的活動。而山下挖有許多隧道，前5次核試據信都在這兒進行。<br />\n<br />\n美國洛薩拉摩斯國家實驗所（Los Alamos National Laboratory）的科學家最近歸納道，萬塔山可承受高達282千噸的核爆，約比廣島核爆強20倍。<br />\n<br />\n自2013年末以來，為挖掘隧道而堆積的岩石碎片已可覆蓋一個足球場，並已堆得相當高。最近有跡象顯示，挖掘工作已放緩，而這很可能顯示，平壤已經準備好進行下一次核試。<br />\n<br />\n此外，觀察家還發現，北韓最近從隧道抽出許多水，應該是要保持測試設備乾燥。對隧道作業來說，地下水往往可能導致進度緩慢，並使電子設備短路。"},{"pid":"65d7256c2634239125b92ab6cc9660967d252c1f","tid":199359,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"地下核試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf1ae17a10e27d6581a2fa6dd1bf97588b2d58b","tid":199359,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2452/d2452536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2452%2Fd2452536.jpg&h=5f22b9a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9284b1bd50b39c2c6b98a4daef75f14a20303a4","tid":199359,"uid":87230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"金仔竟然仲未宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9248e5e472abc90ce0fb21a0ff1fb89a9ecd8a1f","tid":199359,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金仔竟然仲未宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢縮唔縮都死"},{"pid":"de6fb58ee8bcba5802e55b5fc9bdc0d14383f98d","tid":199359,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35070bb0c22ab51ce74d4e335663141146bec432","tid":199359,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"記得好似有次將粒核彈搬來搬去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後冇射"},{"pid":"9530803620f57d57a63b25a5c01fb0954dafe303","tid":199359,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"係就快唔好等下禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5192ec5715fda235076885319d1feb75be1cd1d5","tid":199359,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金仔竟然仲未宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢縮唔縮都死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n欲加之罪 何患無辭，金仔唔縮，搏美國佬唔夠膽仲好。"},{"pid":"1b10dc81ea11429ae2e47329e88ca4becd0d41e7","tid":199359,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>金仔竟然仲未宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢縮唔縮都死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n欲加之罪 何患無辭，金仔唔縮，搏美國佬唔夠膽仲好。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輿論.. 美國佬最怕既係國內輿論，唔係夠唔夠膽開戰問題<br />\n而家風頭火勢上再核試，同自殺冇分別"}]}